             was indicted for <rs id="t18190421-93-off520" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18190421-93-off520" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18190421-93-off520" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18190421-93-cd521" type="crimeDate">12th of March</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18190421-93-off520 t18190421-93-cd521"></join>, one hat, value 15 s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18190421-93-victim1062" type="victimName">
                     Christopher 
                     Swann
                  <interp inst="t18190421-93-victim1062" type="surname" value="Swann"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18190421-93-victim1062" type="given" value="Christopher"></interp>
