                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18190421-93-defend1060 t18190421-93-punish524"></join>
               Whipped
            </rs>, and Discharged.</p>
               <p>First Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Common Sergeant.</p>
